info.name: OldDays colors for Kwakwunderland
info.description: Remember the old Kwakwunderland 2017-2019 design? Since then, the site has changed a lot and although this theme does not completely revert the old design, it makes the site more familiar. For better experience copy CSS-code to Stylebot extension. Due to the nature of Kwakwunderland, not all elements can be changed correctly using themes and extensions.
